            <ul>
                <li><b>Text</b> Messaging.</li>
                <li><b>Voice</b> Streaming.</li>
                <li>Sending <b>memes</b>.</li>
                <li>User can join with name and a secret <b>room ID</b>.</li>
                <li>Shows <b>mic status</b> of users.</li>
                <li>Notify all users if
                    some one <b>left</b> or <b>joins</b> the group(Room).</li>
                <li>Notify all users if someone <b>starts
                        typing</b>.</li>
                <li>Also notify all
                    users if someone <b>starts or stops</b> voice streaming.</li>
                <li>Also shows the <b>status of any message</b>(ie.
                    sending/sent).</li>
                <li>Notify user if he/she <b>lost connection</b> from the server and also <b>reconnects automaticaly</b>
                    if
                    internet connection is restored.</li>
                <li>Also have some default <b>animated emojis.</b></li>
                <li>Very simple and attravtive user interface.</li>

            </ul>
